snippet.title: Puppet Master The Game - Official Announcement - Trailer (2021)
snippet.description:
October Games and Full Moon Features proudly introduce Puppet Master: The Game! 

This Free to Play online multiplayer game will celebrate the series' 30 year legacy. Revisit iconic locations, Select from a large roster of playable characters from the movies. With a variety of online multiplayer game modes supporting up to 8 players, each inspired by the Puppet’s many adventures.

Become the Master of André Toulon’s Puppets in late 2022

Follow us on Twitter:  https://twitter.com/PuppetMasterTG
Follow us on Twitter:  https://twitter.com/Octobergames
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/octobergamesstudio/
